  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "HR Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Provide day to day support in general HR administration and procedures for HR Department.</li><li>Involves in recruitment, collates employment documents, maintains and update the HR personnel files.</li><li>Update new hire information into HR database.</li><li>Filing and scanning of documents.</li><li>Managing onboarding and offboarding processes for employees.</li><li>Worker onboarding and dormitory coordination.</li><li>Work Pass and MOM administration (OFWAS, PCP, Security Bond, FWMI, Appointment, etc)</li><li>Payroll processing and administration</li><li>Responsible for work pass and site pass administration such as pass applications, renewal, cancellation and issuance</li><li>Administer training related matters including coordination or enrolment of internal & external courses, update and maintain training record etc.</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned.<br /></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p></p><ul><li>Prefer 1 year relevant of working experience, preferably in the construction industry.​</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Attention to detail and problem-solving</li><li>Willing to work in construction site office</li><li>Team player.</li><li>Motivated to learn.</li></ul>",
